Package: dataCollectR
Title: Data Collector from Public Databases
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "H. Melike",
           family = "Donertas",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "donertas.melike@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9788-6535"))
Description: This package is essentially a wrapper for multiple R packages to
    retrieve data from public domain. The focus is on data related to ageing,
    microbiome, and computational biology research. The package involves 
    functions to download, tidy, document data as well as to perform basic ID
    conversions and ortholog mapping, utilizing other packages. 
